            "id": "5e09bbef4bb28512a342c470",
            "uuid": "1549ce17-4f26-4924-af67-ba1012a04245",
            "title": "The Compound Power of Doing Nothing!",
            "slug": "wfh-habits-2",
            "html": "<h3 id=\"-and-the-spirit-moved-on-the-surface-of-the-waters\"><em>‚Ä¶And the Spirit Moved on the Surface of the Waters</em></h3><p>Dear Ark-Builder,</p><p>Welcome to a New Quarter. We have been working on features that would make InvestNaira, an Institution you would be proud of Long-Term. Our goal is to build a Wealth-Compounding Ark, that succeeds generations! As long as the Earth Remains.</p><p>No farmer plants a seed and goes every day, digging out to check it‚Äôs growth. It would die! But wait and water, then you see results. First the blade, then the ear, after that, the full corn in the ear.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/900/0*lxtJsM7aJK7WdYKL\" class=\"kg-image\"><figcaption>‚ÄúThe daffodils grow by Compounding‚Äù by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@ruxandramateiu?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-href=\"https://unsplash.com/@ruxandramateiu?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" class=\"markup--anchor markup--figure-anchor\" rel=\"photo-creator noopener noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Ruxandra Mateiu</a> on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unsplash.com?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-href=\"https://unsplash.com?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" class=\"markup--anchor markup--figure-anchor\" rel=\"photo-source noopener noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Unsplash</a></figcaption></figure><p><strong>DOING NOTHING COMPOUNDS WEALTH</strong></p><p><em>‚ÄúIt is not necessary to do extraordinary things to get extraordinary results.‚Äù</em></p><p><em>-Warren Buffet</em></p><p>In the area of Investing, count on us to Do-Nothing, most times! Nothing, but just working hard to sit-tight while we grow wealth! That is exactly what we would be doing with your Seed-Capital. And kindly don‚Äôt be put-off with the assiduity of our inactivity. We are disciples of Charlie Munger.</p><p><em>‚ÄúAssiduity is the ability to sit and do nothing until a great opportunity presents itself‚Äù</em></p><p><em>‚Äì Charlie Munger</em></p><p>In the field of Wealth management, especially, we have stumbled on the secret as proved by these men:</p><p><strong>Sit Down &amp; Do nothing!</strong></p><p>Both men, by not trying to figure out extra-ordinary things, compounded wealth 20.9% yearly for 52 years. Bringing that home, if you had invested NGN100 with Berkshire Hathaway, their flagship Investment Institution, in 1965, it would have grown 2,404,748% in 2017.</p><p>All by the Simplicity of Doing Nothing, Investing Less and Compounding More! So if at anytime, we are asked our strategy to build the most enduring brand in the World, our reply would be:</p><blockquote><strong>Save. | Invest. | Do-Nothing. | Repeat.</strong></blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/900/0*4NVh9dVDOFycUhEW\" class=\"kg-image\"><figcaption>‚ÄúThe Blade, Ear &amp; Full Corn‚Äù by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@technobulka?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-href=\"https://unsplash.com/@technobulka?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" class=\"markup--anchor markup--figure-anchor\" rel=\"photo-creator noopener noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Stanislav Kondratiev</a> on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://unsplash.com?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-href=\"https://unsplash.com?utm_source=medium&amp;utm_medium=referral\" class=\"markup--anchor markup--figure-anchor\" rel=\"photo-source noopener noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Unsplash</a></figcaption></figure><p><strong>RETURNS Q3</strong></p><p>Our returns this quarter was <strong>7.29%</strong>. We are determined to continue to only invest in what we understand. Investing in what we do not understand is trying to do extra-ordinary things. We heed Mr. Buffet‚Äôs advice, <em>do ordinary things and allow them compound to extraordinary returns!</em></p><p>We would love to add a caveat here. Do not Judge us by the monthly, quarterly or yearly returns. That is the natural <em>ups &amp; downs </em>of the financial markets we are invested in. But, judge us by our ability to Save, Invest &amp; Compound as we DoNothing with you for the long haul.</p><p>How would you like to have a compounded interest of 2,000,000% in your own lifetime?</p><p>Well, what you waiting for? Ask others to come on-board the Financial Ark!</p><p>And thank you for Doing-Nothing, as you build with Us, for the Long-Term!</p><p>Ark Builders.<br>Toni &amp; Ebube</p><hr>",
