            "uuid": "dac256d5-cb94-4e82-b734-bae0feedbc40",
            "title": "Millionaire A Decade ‚Äî MAD ARK: FAQs",
            "slug": "mad-millionaire-a-decade",
            "html": "<p>All you need to know to emerge a Millionaire at the end of this decade. Silently. Quietly. Consistently!</p><p>Hi,</p><p>We just challenged you, this year, despite all that is, and would, happen, to decide to be a millionaire this decade. We call it the M.A.D - Millionaire A Decade - Challenge. </p><p>We put up the MAD ‚Äî Millionaire A Decade ‚Äî challenge to raise a million millionaires by the end of this decade. In figures, that is 1 followed by 12 Zeros ‚Äî 1 Trillion ‚Äî in the cumulative amount that we would have built together. And why! Thank you for believing in the <a href=\"http://investnaira.com/#calculator\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">MAD ‚Äî Challenge.</a></p><p>We have culled up a number of FAQs to clear doubts on the MAD ‚Äî Challenge.</p><h2 id=\"frequently-asked-questions-faqs-for-millionaire-a-decade-mad-challenge\"><strong>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) for Millionaire A Decade ‚Äî MAD ‚Äî Challenge</strong></h2><p><em><em><strong><strong>What is the Millionaire A Decade ‚Äî MAD ‚Äî Challenge?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>The Millionaire a Decade ‚Äî MAD ‚Äî is a challenge to raise a million millionaires within a decade. This is in sync with our vision to build multi-generational wealth.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>What is required to be part of the MAD ‚Äî Challenge?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>3 Traits are required. A consistent savings habit, of delayed gratification, on a monthly basis; a long-term, minimum 10 years, investment horizon; and a compounding mindset that brings about wealth.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>How do I join the MAD ‚Äî Challenge?</strong></strong></em></em></p><ol><li><strong><strong>Signup Up </strong></strong>for an <a href=\"http://investnaira.com/Signup\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Invest Naira Account here</a></li><li>On the dashboard, create a <strong><strong>New Goal </strong></strong>titled ‚ÄúMillionaire A Decade ‚Äî MAD‚Äù</li><li>Set the <strong><strong>maturity </strong></strong>to 10 Years ‚Äî Dec 31, 2030.</li><li>Insert the <strong><strong>goal amount </strong></strong>based on the monthly commitment you can stick to. For instance, if you are sticking to N10,000, monthly, then the goal would be N4,170,087.</li><li>Insert your card details for a recurring deposit instruction every month. If you want to do transfers manually, the account details are available on the dashboard.</li><li>Don‚Äôt signup for the <strong><strong>MAD Ark </strong></strong>alone, share and setup for your BFF, Family, Children, and Friends.</li></ol><p><em><em><strong><strong>Do I have to save consistently for 10 years?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>Yes, the goal is to be a millionaire within a decade. So yes, you should save for a minimum of 10 years. Figures in year 10 are projected figures based on calculations and not cast in stone.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>How much can I start with?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>For the MAD Challenge, a minimum NGN5,000 set aside monthly is required to achieve millionaire status.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>Can I aim for more ‚Äî multi-millionaire, centi-millionaire?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>Of course, be our guest. We dare you to step up to the plate, emerge a billionaire at the end of the decade!</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>Can I continue to build my MAD ‚Äî Account once I reach the millionaire threshold?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>Oh, yes! We encourage you to be so rich, you can travel to any country in the world and be a millionaire in that currency. Below, we culled out the top destinations visited by Nigerians and their exchange rate equivalent to attain millionaire status in the destination currency.<br>So take it away, and let‚Äôs be millionaires anywhere in the world. Including space. Picture each number scaled as unlocking a new stage in Super Mario! We would love to have you clocking stage 9 ‚Äî Mars (Space X), at the end of the decade!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://nairasense.investnaira.com/content/images/2020/07/image-2.png\" class=\"kg-image\"><figcaption>What‚Äôs required to achieve millionaire status in destination countries saving a fixed amount for 10 years</figcaption></figure><p><em><em><strong><strong>Is the return guaranteed for the 10 year period?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>No, it is not. Our figures are based on an estimate of 1.8% per month or 24% compounded per year. Figures would fluctuate on a monthly, quarterly and yearly basis. We do not guarantee it, but we are confident the ride to the million a decade would be worth every month journeyed.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>Can I withdraw if I am no longer interested?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>Yes, you can. However, you are giving up on the opportunity to be a millionaire by the end of the decade. Withdrawals are subject to terms and conditions.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>How am I sure one day, InvestNaira would not sink?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>There is a risk in this voyage, like any other voyage in renaissance times. But we appreciate your companionship on this ark building journey. We are a company building Multi-Generational Wealth. We started with Zero. Today, over 2000 clients have signed up to build their Financial Ark with us. Our goal is that by the end of this decade, Dec. 2030, a million of our clients would be millionaires in any currency of their choice. That‚Äôs why we are building!</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>What would the Monies be Invested In?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>We would invest in assets, commodities, industries and any other vehicles that would give a risk-adjusted min. positive internal return threshold.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>Why should I build with you?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>We are Ark Builders, not snake Oil Salesmen. Our Core Values ‚Äî Faith System ‚Äî S.A.G.E speaks truth to our mission.</p><ul><li><strong><strong>Stewardship </strong></strong>‚Äî Accountability &amp; Integrity. We are stewards in all that we do.</li><li><strong><strong>Alacrity </strong></strong>‚Äî Resourcefulness, and Adaptability. We are not afraid to match our 10x goals with 100x action.</li><li><strong><strong>Grit </strong></strong>‚Äî Passion and Perseverance. We never give up. We never-say-never. We would out-work, out-do &amp; out-compete our last trough.</li><li><strong><strong>Energy </strong></strong>‚Äî From Zero to Billion. Impossibility is something we are excited about. From Nothing, Everything Is.</li></ul><p>Lastly, we would be glad to have you on this journey to build with us!</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>Are there any other risks Involved?</strong></strong></em></em></p><p>Oh yes, the risk that the Ship would sink. And all monies would be lost. As Ark Builders, be rest assured that we would be the last to leave the ship. But we are building a Noah‚Äôs Ark, not another Titanic.</p><p><em><em><strong><strong>Thank you for being our first MAD Ark Millionaire!</strong></strong></em></em></p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/60/0*Inf251Z4-GRIqUfy?q=20\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"Image for post\"></figure><p>We B.U.I.L.D,</p><p>Your Ark Builders | Team InvestNaira</p><p>Do not take our word for it, here our Clients <a href=\"http://facebook.com/InvestNaira.\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">here</a></p><h2></h2>",
