: 50%; height: 12.5px; width: 12.5px; transform: translateX(9px) translateY(-18px);\"></div></div><div style=\"margin-left: 8px;\"> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;\"></div> <div style=\" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg)\"></div></div><div style=\"margin-left: auto;\"> <div style=\" width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);\"></div> <div style=\" background-color: #F4F4F4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);\"></div> <div style=\" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);\"></div></div></div></a> <p style=\" margin:8px 0 0 0; padding:0 4px;\"> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CANnWNLj6-v/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" style=\" color:#000; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none; word-wrap:break-word;\" target=\"_blank\">You may not necessarily have the best of education, but this should never stop you from pursuing your aspirations. Mrs Folorunsho Alakija is a true inspiration to us all as Nigerians and people around the globe  #folorunshoalakija #alakija #didyouknowfacts #nigerian #fridayinspiration #tgifriday #consistent #hardwork #wealthmindset #businessmindset #savingmoney #buildingwealth #longtermgoals #effort #entrepreneur #nigerianbusiness #youcandoittooüí™ #investnaira</a></p> <p style=\" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;\">A post shared by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/investnaira/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading\" style=\" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px;\" target=\"_blank\"> InvestNaira</a> (@investnaira) on <time style=\" font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px;\" datetime=\"2020-05-15T14:59:25+00:00\">May 15, 2020 at 7:59am PDT</time></p></div></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"//www.instagram.com/embed.js\"></script><figcaption>Wealth Compounds.&nbsp;</figcaption></figure><p><strong>From Thousands to Billions to Trillions on an Empire!</strong></p><p>And just like JB I want to challenge you to begin fortuitously on this multi-decade journey to wealth! <a href=\"https://InvestNaira.com/signup\" rel=\"noopener\">With us, of-course!</a></p><p>So what would you do in this final week of the seventh month when our Father in the Lord is doing 5 trillion something in a day?</p><p>Simple!</p><ol><li>Start a regular savings plan on your <a href=\"https://www.investnaira.com/dashboard/overview\" rel=\"noopener\">IN Dashboard</a>.</li><li>Label it <strong>JB‚Ää‚Äî‚Ää2046 Billionaire </strong>and set up a minimum regular savings amount.</li><li>Choose either <em>Conservative, Balanced or Aggressive </em>funds!</li><li>Sit down and relax till 2046, allowing it to compound.</li><li>And boom, you would be worth a couple of billions. Naira or Dollars, the currency choice is up to you.</li></ol><p>I know f‚Äôsure, that if you save up to 250,000 NGN, start at 31 and invest it to earn a compounding annual growth rate of about 45% yearly, guess what? Well, when you are 56 years -circa 2046‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääyou would be worth 250 billion Naira, <a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/billionaires/\" rel=\"noopener\">like the JB</a>.</p><p><em>If you doubt that we would make you a billion, well, Wait &amp; See!</em></p><p>Remember, Fortunes Favors the Brave!</p><p><em>Your 999,000% Ark Builder,</em></p><p>Bolu &amp; the ArkBuilding Team,</p><p><em>PS: <a href=\"https://Relentless.com\" rel=\"noopener\">T</a>ype Relentless.com in a browse and see what it gives you. </em></p><hr>",
